<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Spacebar | Feed]]></title><description><![CDATA[My Blog]]></description><link>https://jungwoo0716.github.io</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2020 15:26:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[고분자를 생성하는 방법 - 중합반응(Polymerization)]]></title><description><![CDATA[고분자(Polymer) 분자의 크기에 따라 분자량이 1,000 이하이면 저분자, 10,000 이상이면 고분자로 분류한다. 고분자는 단량체(monomer…]]></description><link>https://jungwoo0716.github.io/polymer-formation/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://jungwoo0716.github.io/polymer-formation/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h2 id=&quot;고분자polymer&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#%EA%B3%A0%EB%B6%84%EC%9E%90polymer&quot; aria-label=&quot;고분자polymer permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;고분자(Polymer)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;분자의 크기에 따라 분자량이 1,000 이하이면 저분자, 10,000 이상이면 고분자로 분류한다. 고분자는 단량체(monomer)라고 불리는 작은 분자가 수백에서 수천개씩 공유결합으로 연결되어 만들어진다.
단량체로부터 고분자를 생성하는 반응을 중합(Polymerization)반응이라고 한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;고분자는 결국 단량체를 기본으로 하기 때문에, 단량체의 구조에 따라 중합 반응이 다르다. 중합반응은 크게 3가지로 나눌 수 있다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;1-작용기functional-group를-갖는-화합물&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-%EC%9E%91%EC%9A%A9%EA%B8%B0functional-group%EB%A5%BC-%EA%B0%96%EB%8A%94-%ED%99%94%ED%95%A9%EB%AC%BC&quot; aria-label=&quot;1 작용기functional group를 갖는 화합물 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1. 작용기(functional group)를 갖는 화합물&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;작용기(functional group)는 유기화합물의 화학적 성질을 결정하는 원자단이다.
예를 들면 아세트산은 &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-mathml&quot;&gt;&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;semantics&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;–&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;mi&gt;C&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;H&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;annotation encoding=&quot;application/x-tex&quot;&gt;\text{--}COOH&lt;/annotation&gt;&lt;/semantics&gt;&lt;/math&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;–&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.07153em;&quot;&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.08125em;&quot;&gt;H&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 카복시기(Carboxyl Group)를 갖고 있고, 에틸알코올은 &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-mathml&quot;&gt;&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;semantics&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;–&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;H&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;annotation encoding=&quot;application/x-tex&quot;&gt;\text{--}OH&lt;/annotation&gt;&lt;/semantics&gt;&lt;/math&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;–&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.08125em;&quot;&gt;H&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 하이드록시기(Hydroxy Group)를 갖고 있다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;&quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/static/a52fcaee071186c216717c5d323161ee/f2bd9/image1.png&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 45.39813857290589%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;image1&quot;
        title=&quot;image1&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/a52fcaee071186c216717c5d323161ee/799d3/image1.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/a52fcaee071186c216717c5d323161ee/00d96/image1.png 148w,
/static/a52fcaee071186c216717c5d323161ee/0b23c/image1.png 295w,
/static/a52fcaee071186c216717c5d323161ee/799d3/image1.png 590w,
/static/a52fcaee071186c216717c5d323161ee/2a3d6/image1.png 885w,
/static/a52fcaee071186c216717c5d323161ee/f2bd9/image1.png 967w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1개의 아세트산과 1개의 에틸알콜올을 가열하면, &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-mathml&quot;&gt;&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;semantics&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;–&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;mi&gt;C&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;H&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;annotation encoding=&quot;application/x-tex&quot;&gt;\text{--}COOH&lt;/annotation&gt;&lt;/semantics&gt;&lt;/math&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;–&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.07153em;&quot;&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.08125em;&quot;&gt;H&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 와 &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-mathml&quot;&gt;&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;semantics&gt;&lt;mrow&gt;&lt;mtext&gt;–&lt;/mtext&gt;&lt;mi&gt;O&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mi&gt;H&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;annotation encoding=&quot;application/x-tex&quot;&gt;\text{--}OH&lt;/annotation&gt;&lt;/semantics&gt;&lt;/math&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;–&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.02778em;&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord mathdefault&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.08125em;&quot;&gt;H&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 사이의 반응으로 물이 제거되면서 에스테르 화합물인 에틸아세테이트가 생성되며, 반응은 더 이상 진행되지 않고 정지된다.
&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;&quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/f2bd9/Polymerization2.png&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 21.199586349534645%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAjUlEQVQY03VP7QoDIQzz/Z9SRP+oiIie33ZL4QYbt0KVJmmbCnrHnJP23vQU55yveq31V4sQeLTW1FpjYUqJM8ZIvXcWgfPe0xiDQgjMQYtlwK7rYhx9AmDOmZxzTECAGvjtDs0YDnelFB4IDTBwuBAcfgESDpG3I2BKKR7+e761lrVSSqq1fjhjDC95AZcOOAePvPJbAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;Polymerization2&quot;
        title=&quot;Polymerization2&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/799d3/Polymerization2.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/00d96/Polymerization2.png 148w,
/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/0b23c/Polymerization2.png 295w,
/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/799d3/Polymerization2.png 590w,
/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/2a3d6/Polymerization2.png 885w,
/static/9468e7fd7316818d59234a6253cd31be/f2bd9/Polymerization2.png 967w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;center&gt;[화학 반응식]&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이와 같이 두 종류의 단량체로부터 물 등의 간단한 분자가 제거되면서 고분자를 생성하는 반응을 중축합(Polycondensation)이라고 한다. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;2-불포화-결합을-갖는-화합물&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#2-%EB%B6%88%ED%8F%AC%ED%99%94-%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%A9%EC%9D%84-%EA%B0%96%EB%8A%94-%ED%99%94%ED%95%A9%EB%AC%BC&quot; aria-label=&quot;2 불포화 결합을 갖는 화합물 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;2. 불포화 결합을 갖는 화합물&lt;/h3&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[인간이 색채를 인식하는 방법]]></title><description><![CDATA[이 포스트는 테스트용입니다.]]></description><link>https://jungwoo0716.github.io/color-recognition-process/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://jungwoo0716.github.io/color-recognition-process/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;이 포스트는 테스트용입니다.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tag, 태그 게시물 예제]]></title><description><![CDATA[게시물에 태그를 지정할 수 있습니다. 해당 게시물의 Markdown YAML Front matter은 아래와 같습니다. 가이드의 Markdown YAML Front matter를 참고하세요. 자세한 가이드는 Documents를 확인해주세요.]]></description><link>https://jungwoo0716.github.io/tag-post-example/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://jungwoo0716.github.io/tag-post-example/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 1991 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;게시물에 태그를 지정할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;해당 게시물의 Markdown YAML Front matter은 아래와 같습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;---
title: Tag, 태그 게시물 예제
date: 2019-07-30
tags:
  - tag
  - 태그
---&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;가이드의 Markdown YAML Front matter를 참고하세요.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;자세한 가이드는 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/junhobaik/junhobaik.github.io/wiki/Document-(Borderless)&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;Documents&lt;/a&gt;를 확인해주세요.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Image, 이미지 게시물 예제]]></title><description><![CDATA[이미지 파일이 첨부된 게시물의 예제입니다. 폴더를 만들고 폴더의 제목이 해당 게시물의 주소가 됩니다. 게시물 파일명은 index.md 로 합니다. 이미지 파일은 폴더 내에 위치시킵니다. 자세한 가이드는 Documents를 확인해주세요.]]></description><link>https://jungwoo0716.github.io/image-post-example.md copy/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://jungwoo0716.github.io/image-post-example.md copy/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 1991 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span
      class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-wrapper&quot;
      style=&quot;position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;&quot;
    &gt;
      &lt;a
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-link&quot;
    href=&quot;/static/483b2386e38636bd5d9e7357b4c6796b/67270/screenshot.png&quot;
    style=&quot;display: block&quot;
    target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    rel=&quot;noopener&quot;
  &gt;
    &lt;span
    class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-background-image&quot;
    style=&quot;padding-bottom: 66.58031088082902%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;&quot;
  &gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;img
        class=&quot;gatsby-resp-image-image&quot;
        alt=&quot;screenshot&quot;
        title=&quot;screenshot&quot;
        src=&quot;/static/483b2386e38636bd5d9e7357b4c6796b/799d3/screenshot.png&quot;
        srcset=&quot;/static/483b2386e38636bd5d9e7357b4c6796b/00d96/screenshot.png 148w,
/static/483b2386e38636bd5d9e7357b4c6796b/0b23c/screenshot.png 295w,
/static/483b2386e38636bd5d9e7357b4c6796b/799d3/screenshot.png 590w,
/static/483b2386e38636bd5d9e7357b4c6796b/2a3d6/screenshot.png 885w,
/static/483b2386e38636bd5d9e7357b4c6796b/ae92f/screenshot.png 1180w,
/static/483b2386e38636bd5d9e7357b4c6796b/67270/screenshot.png 1544w&quot;
        sizes=&quot;(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px&quot;
        style=&quot;width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;&quot;
        loading=&quot;lazy&quot;
      /&gt;
  &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이미지 파일이 첨부된 게시물의 예제입니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;폴더를 만들고 폴더의 제목이 해당 게시물의 주소가 됩니다.&lt;/p&gt;
